data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. New! New! New! UNDER appraisal value!!! INSTANT equity!!! Introducing your new haven in the highly sought-after Panther Trace community. This home has been lovingly cared for and thoughtfully updated, presenting a true gem awaiting your arrival. As you start your day with a cup of coffee on the charming front porch, you'll immediately embrace the sense of community that surrounds you. The house itself exudes a fresh appeal, with a recently painted exterior that beckons you inside to explore further. Once indoors, you'll find a well-maintained interior featuring new flooring and a fresh coat of paint, all completed in 2020. The kitchen, the heart of the home, boasts smart appliances that not only simplify cooking but also infuse a modern touch. The master bedroom offers dual sinks and a convenient walk-in closet, making daily routines a breeze. To add a cozy and inviting ambiance, a custom master detail wall with accent lighting has been thoughtfully added. In 2021, the house received upgrades including a new roof and an enhanced kitchen. A privacy-enhancing fence was also installed, elevating the overall appeal. Perfect oversized garage for all your toys or storage needs. The community, complete with a pool and playground, offers an abundance of amenities. Moreover, excellent schools are within easy reach. The AC system was recently replaced in 2023, ensuring year-round comfort. The backyard, perfect for various outdoor activities, has been thoughtfully revitalized with a new back porch, pavers, and an inviting patio that includes a fire pit area – a perfect setting for entertaining. The backyard itself provides ample space for a range of outdoor activities, while the new sod adds a burst of life to the landscape.  This home effortlessly combines modern updates with comfort. Meticulously maintained and thoughtfully upgraded, it is move-in ready, offering a warm and inviting place to call home.
